_sText:
A mid sized map made of 2 locations 1st the Eiffel tower and 2nd Tour Montparnasse in Paris.
When you reach end of the climbing you can activate and enjoy the fireworks at the Eiffel tower.
There is also a training area which contains : long jumping, bunnyhop, strafe and crouch jump areas.

Big thanks to map testers:
d347hm4n and FalseProphet

I hope you will enjoy and have fun while playing the map.
